ocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hiv1665703123012.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hiv1665703123012.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hiv1665703123012.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hiv1665703123012\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     Component Instance Properties</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hiv1665703123012__sidenav-submenue8639baa-9770-4d6d-82b7-4a41778b1237\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kfu1665702580321.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kfu1665702580321.html\" title=\"Specifies a comma-separated string that defines the position and size of the form window in pixels.\">Dimension</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gsr1665702580242.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gsr1665702580242.html\" title=\"Sets the component instance to display-only, meaning that data cannot be modified using structure editor functions. Valid values are True or False (default)\">Display</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fhz1665703123388.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fhz1665703123388.html\" title=\"Form instance property of a popup form that specifies the field to which the popup window is bound. This can be the name of any field in the current form instance. This property can be set in ProcScript using newinstance. If not specified, the default is the current field.\">FieldName</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yte1665702580476.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yte1665702580476.html\" title=\"Determines whether the form instance can lose focus without being closed. Valid values are Modal or Non-Modal (instance can lose and get focus)\">Modality</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tfe1665702580397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tfe1665702580397.html\" title=\"Determines whether the component instance can only be used to retrieve, but not modify, data. When True, data can only be entered as a retrieve profile.\">Query</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ico1665702529641.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ico1665702529641.html\" title=\"Determines whether a transaction group is created for the DBMS I/O associated with this component instance and all instances started from it. Valid values are True or False.\">Transaction</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zxd1665702773590.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zxd1665702773590.html\" title=\"Window property that determines the position and size state of the Form window. Setting state takes precedence over setting position and size properties. Use $windowproperties to set state.\">state</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"imm1665702580556.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/imm1665702580556.html\" title=\"Component instance property of a non-modal form that determines whether it immediately gets input focus. It can only be set when using newinstance.\">InitialFocus</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613500\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\